name: Cat Lingerie (cat cutout, panties, thighhighs)
description:
Cat lingerie concepts trained on 104 unique images. Does cat cutout and cat ear lingerie very well. cat ear thighhighs was more of an afterthought and wasn't really trained too well, but still sometimes works.

When using the trigger words, combine them with the article of clothing + colour you want applied. ie: "cleavage cutout, red bra" or cat ear "panties, black panties". Note that this doesn't always work and you may need to manually edit the colours with inpainting. Apparently cat cutout works on more than just bras although I wasn't initially training it for that purpose. If you're using for it for clothing other than bras, tack on cleavage cutout and cleavage.

Because there was so many images of actual cat girls or girls wearing cat ears in the training set, use a combination of cat ears, cat girl, animal ears, tail, etc in the negative prompt if you don't want those features.

Seems to work well with character loras and was tested on Anything and AbyssOrangeMix.

You can use the sample prompts as a rough guide.
